“VM(s) required to host below components”

Components to Mention

Spring Boot application hosting

React UI hosting

Jenkins CI/CD

Oracle Database

Logs, backups, monitoring



We request infrastructure support for setting up environments required for application development and deployment.

The setup includes:

Hosting Spring Boot backend services

Hosting React-based UI

Jenkins for CI/CD pipeline execution

Oracle Database for application data

Kindly provision VM(s) as per organizational standards, security, and best practices for these components.
